headline: Got $300? Buy These 3 Top Dividend Stocks and Never Look Back.
summary: Realty Income (NYSE: O), Johnson & Johnson (NYSE: JNJ), and Brookfield Infrastructure (NYSE: BIPC)(NYSE: BIP) have elite records of growing their higher-yielding dividends.  Realty Income's mission is to deliver dependable monthly dividends to its investors that grow over time.  With 657 consecutive monthly dividends paid since its founding and 130 dividend increases since its public market listing three decades ago, the real estate investment trust (REIT) has been very successful in achieving its mission.
